release.changelog: With this update, Device Center gets a brand new look. We have added a new feature for Plus users. Wi-Fi Security scans the security protocol of the Wi-Fi network you are connected to and informs you whether it is secure or not. The hardware monitoring feature has now been removed. We have added a redirect to our Device Care application for more advanced hardware monitoring and system information.
